divs: Sighting DetailsFirst thought - a big meteorite coming down burning in the air then - a burning plane but when the trajectory become smoothly changing from down to horizontal and then slightly upward I understood it was not a meteorite. then it went slightly upward fromn me into the dark sky. sorry, no photos
